OKLEBE baphenya icala lokubulawa kwephoyisa lesifazane elineminyaka engu-25, okuthiwa lidutshulwe ngumlisa ongaziwa ngoLwesihlanu, kwa- E, eMlaza. Kuthiwa iphoyisa elinguConstable Portia Mhlanga, belisebenzela esiteshini esikuleli lokishi. Beliselivini ngenkathi lihlaselwa. Kubikwa ukuthi kuqhamuke umsolwa obhekise isibhamu ngakulo, lisalinde isoka lalo emotweni. Umsolwa kubikwa ukuthi udubule amahlandla amahlanu, maqede wanyamalala emehlweni. UCaptain Simphiwe Mhlongo, okhulumela oKlebe, uthe ithimba lophiko lobugebengu obuhleliwe eThekwini, limatasa nophenyo lokubulawa kwephoyisa. “Imbangela yokubulawa kwalo ayikaziwa. Akukaboshwa muntu,” kubeka uCapt Mhlongo. Umufi ubelinde isoka lakhe ebelisangene endaweni yokudla ekuleli lokishi, Ebenvilla ngenkathi kugasela umsolwa okuthiwa umdubule kwesingenhla emzimbeni. Amaphoyisa kubikwa ukuthi athole izinhlamvu ezine endaweni yesigameko. Kuthiwa umufi, ushone esesibhedlela, iPrince Mshiyeni Memorial. 